---
layout: layouts/base.njk
permalink: /404.html
title: "Page introuvable"
eleventyExcludeFromCollections: true
---

<div class="container--narrow" style="padding: 80px 24px; text-align: center;">
    <p style="font-size: 6rem; margin-bottom: 0; line-height: 1;">404</p>
    <h1 class="page-header__title" style="margin-bottom: 12px;">Hors terrain !</h1>
    <p style="font-size: 1.15rem; color: var(--text-light); margin-bottom: 40px; max-width: 500px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">
        La page que vous cherchez n'existe pas ou a été déplacée. Pas de panique, retournez sur le court.
    </p>
    <a href="/" class="header__subscribe-btn" style="display: inline-block; padding: 14px 32px; font-size: 1rem; text-decoration: none;">
        Retour à l'accueil
    </a>

    {% set latestArticles = collections.articles | limit(3) %}
    {% if latestArticles.length > 0 %}
    <section style="margin-top: 64px; text-align: left;">
        <div class="section__header">
            <h2 class="section__title">Articles populaires</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="cards-grid">
            {% for article in latestArticles %}
                {% include "partials/card-article.njk" %}
            {% endfor %}
        </div>
    </section>
    {% endif %}
</div>
